response.yaml_spec:
validate_age:
  evals:
    IsBoolean:
      type: bool
    CorrectLogic:
      assertion: output == (0 <= input <= 150)
  dataset:
  - case:
      id: boundary_lower_zero
      input: 0
      expected: true
  - case:
      id: boundary_upper_150
      input: 150
      expected: true
  - case:
      id: normal_age
      input: 25
      expected: true
  - case:
      id: edge_negative_one
      input: -1
      expected: false
  - case:
      id: edge_above_upper_limit
      input: 151
      expected: false
  - case:
      id: error_extreme_negative
      input: -999999
      expected: false
  - case:
      id: error_extreme_positive
      input: 1000000
      expected: false
